      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't have time to go back to the clinic to talk to them about it right now, it's such a hassle. if i just skip the last week of the dose, what's the worst that actually happens to me personally? like, is it definitely going to come back, or is that just a scary way of saying it might be harder to treat later? i just want to know if it's safe to stop now since i feel perfect.",
